{"word":"περιφύομαι","slug":"περιφύομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>περιφύομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>mid.</a> <el>-φύσομαι</el>) (<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <el>περιπέφῡκα</el>,) (epic <el>-πέφῠα</el>) (aor2 <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <el>περιέφῡν</el>) (<a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <el>περιφῦναι</el>) (<a href='S:participle'>part.</a> <el>-φύς</el> and <el>-φῠείς</el>) (<a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <el>περιφῠῆναι</el>) (<a href='S:participle'>part.</a> <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <el>-φῠείς</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <i>to grow round about</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of persons, <i>to grow round, cling to</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a> or <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; so of shoes, <el>περιέφυσαν Περσικαί τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}